sources.title: Alien Autopsy: Fact or Fiction? Uncut | Unexplained UFOs
sources.description:
Hosted by Jonathan Frakes ("Star Trek"), this classic, original television special investigated footage that was allegedly filmed by the United States military. Airing on television in 1995, the footage initially shocked audiences with depictions of an actual extraterrestrial. In this Uncut version, the team delves deeper than ever before in the search for answers in this extraterrestrial mystery.
